title: Trevor Noah Dating Model Jordyn Taylor
text:
Comments The TV host brought along his new girlfriend Taylor to the premiere of his 'The Daily Show with Trevor Noah' in N.Y.C. last week. 
Trevor Noah has a new leading lady; model Jordyn Taylor. The TV host brought along his girlfriend to the star-studded premiere of his " The Daily Show with Trevor Noah " in N.Y.C. this past Thursday, Oct. 22. According to Us Weekly , the 31-year-old South African comedian first met Taylor after he moved to N.Y.C. earlier this year to begin his new gig as host of "The Daily Show". The outlet, furthermore, reported that Taylor originally hails from L.A. and lives with Noah on the Upper West Side. She works at Ram, modeling in the dealer's auto shows. It was not known though on when the couple began dating. Taylor hasn't shared any photos on social media of them together, but she did share a pic on Instagram of a "Daily Show" ad on a bus in N.Y.C., featuring Noah's face front and center late last month. "Tonight's the night! Tune in," she captioned the image, referring to her boyfriend's debut hosting the show. A photo posted by Jordyn Taylor (@jordyntaylornow) on Sep 28, 2015 at 9:53am PDT
